code: @Test public void testManagedNamePattern() throws Exception {     getMockEndpoint("mock:result").expectedMessageCount(1).     template.sendBody("direct:start", "World").     assertMockEndpointsSatisfied().     MBeanServer mbeanServer = context.getManagementStrategy().getManagementAgent().getMBeanServer().     assertEquals("cool-1.2.3", context.getManagementName()).     ObjectName on = ObjectName.getInstance("org.apache.camel:context=localhost/" + context.getManagementName() + ",type=context,name=\"" + context.getName() + "\"").     assertTrue("Should be registered", mbeanServer.isRegistered(on)). }
